KYLES v. WARDEN OF THE MARYLAND HOUSE OF CORRECTION [App. No. 131,

September Term, 1965.]

Decided February 3, 1966.

Before Prescott, C. J., and Hammond, Horney, Marbury, Barnes and McWilliams, JJ.

*711Per Curiam.

Eor the reasons assigned in Judge Mathias’ opinion below, the application for leave to appeal will be denied.

Application for leave to appeal denied.
